   20: -module(erl_internal_SUITE).
   21: 
   22: -export([all/0, suite/0,groups/0,init_per_suite/1, end_per_suite/1, 
   23: 	 init_per_group/2,end_per_group/2]).
   24: 
   25: -export([behav/1]).
   26: 
   27: -export([init_per_testcase/2, end_per_testcase/2]).
   28: 
   29: -include_lib("common_test/include/ct.hrl").
   30: 
   31: suite() ->
   32:     [{ct_hooks,[ts_install_cth]},
   33:      {timetrap,{minutes,2}}].
   34: 
   35: all() -> 
   36:     [behav].
   37: 
   38: groups() -> 
   39:     [].
   40: 
   41: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   42:     Config.
   43: 
   44: end_per_suite(_Config) ->
   45:     ok.
   46: 
   47: init_per_group(_GroupName, Config) ->
   48:     Config.
   49: 
   50: end_per_group(_GroupName, Config) ->
   51:     Config.
   52: 
   53: 
   54: init_per_testcase(_Case, Config) ->
   55:     Config.
   56: 
   57: end_per_testcase(_Case, _Config) ->
   58:     ok.
   59: 
   60: %% Check that the behaviour callbacks are correctly defined.
   61: behav(_) ->
   62:     Modules = [application, gen_server, gen_fsm, gen_event,
   63:                gen_statem, supervisor_bridge, supervisor],
   64:     lists:foreach(fun check_behav/1, Modules).
   65: 
   66: check_behav(Module) ->
   67:     Callbacks = callbacks(Module),
   68:     Optional = optional_callbacks(Module),
   69:     check_behav_list(Callbacks, Module:behaviour_info(callbacks)),
   70:     check_behav_list(Optional, Module:behaviour_info(optional_callbacks)).
   71: 
   72: check_behav_list([], []) -> ok;
   73: check_behav_list([L | L1], L2) ->
   74:     true = lists:member(L, L2),
   75:     L3 = lists:delete(L, L2),
   76:     check_behav_list(L1, L3).
   77: 
   78: callbacks(application) ->
   79:     [{start,2}, {stop,1}];
   80: callbacks(gen_server) ->
   81:     [{init,1}, {handle_call,3}, {handle_cast,2},
   82:      {handle_info,2}, {terminate,2}, {code_change,3},
   83:      {format_status,1}, {format_status,2}, {handle_continue, 2}];
   84: callbacks(gen_fsm) ->
   85:     [{init,1}, {handle_event,3}, {handle_sync_event,4},
   86:      {handle_info,3}, {terminate,3}, {code_change,4},
   87:      {format_status,2}];
   88: callbacks(gen_event) ->
   89:     [{init,1}, {handle_event,2}, {handle_call,2},
   90:      {handle_info,2}, {terminate,2}, {code_change,3},
   91:      {format_status,1}, {format_status,2}];
   92: callbacks(gen_statem) ->
   93:     [{init, 1}, {callback_mode, 0}, {state_name, 3},
   94:      {handle_event, 4}, {terminate, 3}, {code_change, 4},
   95:      {format_status, 1}, {format_status, 2}];
   96: callbacks(supervisor_bridge) ->
   97:     [{init,1}, {terminate,2}];
   98: callbacks(supervisor) ->
   99:     [{init,1}].
  100: 
  101: optional_callbacks(application) ->
  102:     [];
  103: optional_callbacks(gen_server) ->
  104:     [{handle_info, 2}, {handle_continue, 2}, {terminate, 2}, {code_change, 3}, {format_status, 1}, {format_status, 2}];
  105: optional_callbacks(gen_fsm) ->
  106:     [{handle_info, 3}, {terminate, 3}, {code_change, 4}, {format_status, 2}];
  107: optional_callbacks(gen_event) ->
  108:     [{handle_info, 2}, {terminate, 2}, {code_change, 3}, {format_status, 1}, {format_status, 2}];
  109: optional_callbacks(gen_statem) ->
  110:     [{state_name, 3}, {handle_event, 4},
  111:      {terminate, 3}, {code_change, 4}, {format_status, 1}, {format_status, 2}];
  112: optional_callbacks(supervisor_bridge) ->
  113:     [];
  114: optional_callbacks(supervisor) ->
  115:     [].
